oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Two crystalline modifications of 1,1 '-thiobis(2-naphthol)
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: MAGUE, JT
BALAKRISHNA, MS
PUNJI, B
SURESH, D
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The title compound, C20H14O2S, has been obtained in two monoclinic forms, which differ in their unit- cell dimensions, compactness of packing and conformation. Pairwise association of molecules occurs via complementary O-H center dot center dot center dot O hydrogen bonding.
